headline.print_headline: South Dakota: Obama Visits His 50th State
headline.main: Obama, Visiting South Dakota, Checks Off 50th State

snippet: President Obama checked the final state off his to-do list on Friday as he delivered the commencement address at a community college in Watertown, S.D.
